--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 512a72de08c75cf4e8a8424f7b75a271, type: 3}
  m_Name: D4T18_IndianAfterGunFind_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npc: 1
  sequence:
  - dialogueText: I see you found your bonus. A great tool to have in such a place,
      isn't it?
    buttonText: Needed a warning
  - dialogueText: As long as you keep it hidden, you should have no problems. Surprises
      are part of the local tax.
    buttonText: If boss finds out...
  - dialogueText: Then don't show him. I can provide all kinds of stuff if the job
      is worth the effort.
    buttonText: All kinds?
  - dialogueText: I'm the man who gets things done here. You name it, I find a way.
    buttonText: A boat?
  - dialogueText: A boat? Yes, I can do that. But a boat requires a very expensive
      job.
    buttonText: How expensive?
  - dialogueText: It's hard to get a boat here without everyone noticing. We'll talk
      price when the time is right.
    buttonText: I see
  - dialogueText: For now, keep your new friend out of sight. We wouldn't want any
      accidents
    buttonText: Fine
